{"tid":1645321,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對準政權 暴警 係運動唯一出路","createTime":"2019-10-11T00:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:21:12.000Z","uid":256678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e046a08c28c0ecb92f94810bc722d16e436d50","tid":1645321,"uid":256678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:26:02.000Z","msg":"哩個星期見到疲態<br />\n（其實一個月前夠話攰啦 又話咩似傘運後期 結果上星期先開花嚟）<br />\n<br />\n其實攰唔攰同實質做咩嚟無乜關係<br />\n反而要問下我地發力發咗喺邊<br />\n<br />\n裝修 拆交通燈得返嚟嘅feedback的確會令人好灰心<br />\n唔理件事啱定唔岩 啲Feedback係令人覺得最攰<br />\n<br />\n所以行動上要正確<br />\n發力點要啱<br />\n<br />\n去機場 行出青衣都唔會覺得攰<br />\n圍警署 無人覺得攰<br />\n圍政總無人覺得無力<br />\n<br />\n所以 對準政權 暴警先係唯一可行出路"},{"pid":"535995c56679321d0f2690f97a5765d97385dde8","tid":1645321,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:31:29.000Z","msg":"睇左未<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/you-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fyou-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=dd04284f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fyou-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer&h=ee221ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/you-may-say-i-m-a-dreamer</a>"},{"pid":"c7fb84dc26d770076785da8e113d6ce9533839ee","tid":1645321,"uid":258133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WcoEQT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WcoEQT.jpg&h=a6c65c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7399298b2dcf3ad49831a2a85a18322ee9f0bc57","tid":1645321,"uid":264128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:21:12.000Z","msg":"對抗警暴，1011 十八區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644865</a>"}]}